RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

95-1288. State v. Calhoun.

Lorain County, No. 94CA005824. Reported at 73 Ohio St.3d 1441, 654 N.E.2d 352. IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of the dismissal of this case for want of prosecution be, and hereby is, denied, effective October 3, 1995.
